## Go-to-Market Strategy Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the product/service and its unique value
- [ ] 2. Identify and prioritize target segments
- [ ] 3. Develop positioning and messaging framework
- [ ] 4. Define channel strategy (direct, partner, digital)
- [ ] 5. Plan launch sequence and phasing
- [ ] 6. Set success metrics and KPIs
- [ ] 7. Create the GTM plan document

## Key Inputs
- Product/Service: {{product_service}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Target Markets: {{target_markets}}
- Competitive Context: {{competitive_context}}
- Launch Timeline: {{launch_timeline}}
